{"name": "odoo14-addon-purchase-exception", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-purchase-exception", "version": "14.0.1.0.1.dev9", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/purchase-workflow", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo14-addon-base-exception", "odoo"], "summary": "Custom exceptions on purchase order", "upload_time": 1734751407}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fpurchase--workflow-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/purchase-workflow\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/purchase-workflow/tree/14.0/purchase_exception\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/purchase-workflow-14-0/purchase-workflow-14-0-purchase_exception\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/purchase-workflow&target_branch=14.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Purchase Exception\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:521cf913063055a090c75493a5bb64a8227d9e61b1626463f0c102ed6e7ca478\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module allows you attach several customizable exceptions to your\npurchase order in a way that you can filter orders by exceptions type and fix them.\n\nThis is especially useful in an scenario for mass purchases order import, because it's likely some orders have\nerrors when you import them (like product not found in Odoo, wrong line\nformat etc.)\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/purchase-workflow/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/purchase-workflow/issues/new?body=module:%20purchase_exception%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Akretion\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Mourad EL HADJ MIMOUNE \\<<mailto:mourad.elhadj.mimoune@akretion.com>>\n- Sudhir Arya \\<<mailto:sudhir@erpharbor.com>>\n- Kitti U. \\<<mailto:kittiu@ecosoft.co.th>> (migration to v14)\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/purchase-workflow](https://github.com/OCA/purchase-workflow/tree/14.0/purchase_exception) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.wizard", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.wizard.purchase_exception_confirm", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.wizard..purchase_exception_confirm", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.models.exception_rule", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.models..exception_rule", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.models.purchase", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.models..purchase", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.models.purchase_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.models..purchase_line", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.models.exception_rule", "documentation": ["Copyright 2017 Akretion (http://www.akretion.com)", "Copyright 2020 Camptocamp SA", "Mourad EL HADJ MIMOUNE <mourad.elhadj.mimoune@akretion.com>", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.models.exception_rule.ExceptionRule", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.models.exception_rule.ExceptionRule._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.models.exception_rule.ExceptionRule.purchase_ids", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.models.exception_rule.ExceptionRule.model", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_exception.tests", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "cl